content.para1: Part of the BLVCK02 Collection, the 'Bold Stripe Hoodie' features a unique extended stripe across the chest/arms with the Blvck logo printed across the sleeve/chest for a minimalist, streetwear look.
content.para2: Made from luxurious 100% Terry Cotton, all our hoodies are super soft to the touch and perfect for everyday wear.
content.para3: Unisex fit. Fits regular size for men and oversized for women.
